* [[Deployment]] options abound, though the most common by far is LiveCD
* [[Web_Standards]] compliant
* [[Cost_effective]] - try the [free version](http://download.webconverger.com/) or order a [customised version](http://webconverger.com/buy)
* [[No_users_or_registration|Registration]]
* [[Flash_and_PDF_viewer|Adobe]]
* [[Easy_to_use|Training]]
* [[Low_Maintenance|Maintenance]]
* Commercial [[Support]] via [Webconverger.com](http://webconverger.com/) is available. Please enquire.
